Name: UNIT IDENTIFIER OF AGENCY ASSUMING CONTROL
REQUESTING TASKING AUTHORITY
Explanation: NONE

Name: TACTICAL CONTROL AUTHORITY
Explanation: A LISTING OF COMMAND AUTHORITY THAT IS CONTROLLING THE TACTICAL PORTION OF THE MISSION.

Name: ENGAGEMENT AUTHORITY
Explanation: THE AUTHORITY RESPONSIBLE FOR TASKING THE ENGAGEMENT.

Name: DESTINATION UNIT
Explanation: THE NAME OF THE UNIT FOR WHICH MATERIAL IS HELD FOR TRANSFER.

Name: SHORAD IFF ORIGINATING AUTHORITY
Explanation: THE SHORAD ORIGINATING AUTHORITY.

Name: NATO UNDESIGNATED UNIT
Explanation: A UNIT WHICH HAS NOT YET BEEN DESIGNATED BY A NATO ASSET.

Name: GATEWAY CONTROLLING SIDE UNIT IDENTIFIER
Explanation: SEE STANAG 4211.

Name: GATEWAY REQUESTING UNIT IDENTIFIER
Explanation: THE IDENTIFICATION OF THE UNIT THAT REQUESTS ESTABLISHMENT OF A GATEWAY.

Name: GATEWAY RECEIVING UNIT IDENTIFIER
Explanation: THE UNIT TO WHICH A GATEWAY REQUEST IS DIRECTED.

Name: PACKAGE IDENTIFICATION
Explanation: THE ALPHANUMERIC IDENTIFIER THAT JOINS TWO OR MORE ELEMENTS OF COMPOSITE FORCE PACKAGE.

Name: UNIT IDENTIFICATION CODE, SPECIFIC
Explanation: THE UNIQUE IDENTIFICATION OF A UNIT LEVEL ORGANIZATION.

Name: TANKER UNIT REFERENCE NUMBER
Explanation: A REFERENCE NUMBER USED BY THE AIR-TO-AIR-REFUELLING TANKER AIRCRAFT IN A VARIABLE MESSAGE FORMAT (VMF) INTERFACE TO UNIQUELY IDENTIFY THE TANKER AIRCRAFT.

Name: TASKED UNIT NAME
Explanation: THE DESIGNATOR OF THE UNIT THAT IS TASKED TO PERFORM THE MISSION.

Name: DELIVERY UNIT IDENTIFIER
Explanation: THE UNIT IDENTIFIER OF THE UNIT TO WHICH SOMETHING IS TO BE DELIVERED.

Name: AIRCRAFT UNIT REFERENCE NUMBER
Explanation: A REFERENCE NUMBER USED BY THE AIRCRAFT IN A VARIABLE MESSAGE FORMAT (VMF) INTERFACE TO UNIQUELY IDENTIFY THE AIRCRAFT.

Name: FAC UNIT REFERENCE NUMBER
Explanation: A REFERENCE NUMBER USED BY THE FORWARD AIR CONTROLLER (FAC) IN A VARIABLE MESSAGE FORMAT (VMF) INTERFACE TO UNIQUELY IDENTIFY THE FAC.

Name: RECEIVER UNIT REFERENCE NUMBER
Explanation: A REFERENCE NUMBER USED BY THE RECEIVER AIRCRAFT IN A VARIABLE MESSAGE FORMAT (VMF) INTERFACE TO UNIQUELY IDENTIFY THE RECEIVER AIRCRAFT.

Name: UNIT REFERENCE NUMBER
Explanation: A REFERENCE NUMBER USED BY UNITS IN A VARIABLE MESSAGE FORMAT (VMF) INTERFACE TO UNIQUELY IDENTIFY THE FRIENDLY MILITARY UNITS.

Name: ENTITY ID SERIAL NUMBER
Explanation: THE SERIAL NUMBER USED FOR IDENTIFICATION PURPOSES OF AN ENTITY. ESTABLISHED BY THE SYSTEM THAT PROMULGATES AN ENTITY ONTO THE COMMUNICATIONS NET TO IDENTITY THE ENTITY.

Name: UNIT REFERENCE NUMBER_1
Explanation: A UNIT REFERENCE NUMBER USED DURING A SITUATIONAL AWARENESS DATA LINK.
